@h1 Blog Detail
This page displays the details of the blog entry you have clicked on. Under the title of the blog you will see the date the page was created and who/when the blog was last edited by. Underneath the text you will see 5 links the following will tell you what they are about.

@dl
@dt Edit This Entry
@dd
Click this if you would like to edit this blog entry.
@dt New Blog Entry
@dd
Click this if you would like to create a New Blog Entry.
@dt Back
@dd
Click this if you would like to view the previous blog.
@dt Next
@dd
Click this if you would like to view the next blog.
@dt Back To List
@dd
Click this if you would like to view the list of all the blog entries for this blog.
@/dl
